title: Are You Afraid of Dying?
itunes:title: Are You Afraid of Dying?
description:
Episode 134 - What scares you more - dying or living a wasted life? In this episode I talk about death and how I am okay with dying when my day comes because I will know I put everything I had into this life and did everything I could.
